  <!-- EN: insect mandibles -->
  <VRE_InsectMandibles.label>虫族钳颚</VRE_InsectMandibles.label>
  <!-- EN: Very strong, insect-like mandibles, allowing this person to consume food significantly quicker. They will also be able to use these mandibles in combat if unarmed. -->
  <VRE_InsectMandibles.description>这对咬合力相当出色的钳颚不仅可以大幅提高进食速度，在手无寸铁时还能用来战斗。</VRE_InsectMandibles.description>
