  <!-- EN: ripper-blade -->
  <VRE_RipperBlades.label>撕裂镰刃</VRE_RipperBlades.label>
  <!-- EN: A long and deadly ripper-blade that greatly lowers manipulation, while being able to be used in melee combat to rip even armored enemies in half. -->
  <VRE_RipperBlades.description>这对如同刀锋般致命的镰刃会降低操作能力，但在战斗中可以轻易地将身着装甲的敌人撕成碎片。</VRE_RipperBlades.description>
